Imogen Poots https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Imogen_Poots 0 Imogen Poots (born 3 June 1989) is an English actress. She played Tammy in the post-apocalyptic science fiction horror film 28 Weeks Later (2007), Linda Keith in the Jimi Hendrix biopic Jimi: All Is by My Side (2013), Debbie Raymond in the Paul Raymond biopic The Look of Love (2013), and Julia Maddon in the American action movie Need for Speed (2014). In 2016 she starred as Kelly Ann in the Showtime series Roadies. Imogen_Poots ( born 3_June_1989 ) is an_English_actress . She played Tammy in the_post-apocalyptic_science_fiction_horror_film 28_Weeks Later ( 2007_) , Linda_Keith in the_Jimi_Hendrix_biopic_Jimi : All_Is by My_Side ( 2013_) , Debbie_Raymond in the_Paul_Raymond biopic_The_Look of Love_(_2013_) , and Julia_Maddon in the_American_action_movie Need for Speed_(_2014_) .
